  "The problem of finding initial conditions": "",
  "Integrating from 0 to some value": "",
  "Finding a particular antiderivative that satisfies a given condition like F(a) = b": "",
  "An initial value problem provides a differential equation (like F'(x) = f(x)) along with an initial condition (like F(0) = 5). Together, they determine a unique particular antiderivative by fixing the constant C.": "",
